structure.unit: TRAFFIC REGULATIONS -- VEHICLE EQUIPMENT AND STORAGE

law.text: KRS 189.390 shall not apply to emergency vehicles while being operated under the provisions of KRS 189.910 to 189.950.
law.history: Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 177, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1988. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 9, sec. 2, effective March 1, 1974.
